thread.title: TV | First Dates

author: Fiona Flynn
title: TV | First Dates
text: The show where you get to watch the awkwardness of a first date unfold all from the safety of your own couch. Tonight we meet self-confessed nerd Lachlan who strikes gold when he sits down to eat with psychologist Rachel - who turns out to be an avid Star Wars fan. Elsewhere, Nanny and weightlifter Lucy seems to have met her match when her and her date Caroline start lifting each other up... yep. All leads to a bit of wardrobe malfunction too. First dates wha', some craic.
